      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "THE SWIFT ONE (4) drew on the back row and worked home in good style to finish just 1.6 metres from the winner in third last week to make it three placings in a row at this circuit and distance. Her hoof is on the till so could break through here. TASBMIKI (3) made it two wins in succession at this venue last start when he got the cash by 1.8 metres. A nice draw on the front line should ensure a cosy run. Big chance to land the hat trick. PAS DE CHEVAL (2) has finished within 4m of the winner in her last two outings here. Draws for another good showing. GO WITHOUT (8) was solid from this barrier in a higher-graded race last time and recorded back-to-back placings here prior. Player with even luck.",
